      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "Now it's clear, why my own build containing #1479 showed up the balance (left side on the overview window) imediately, as I use `bool IsInMainChain() const { return GetDepthInMainChain() > 0; }` instead of `GetDepthInMainChain() < 2`.\n\nI'm just asking, what is the right approach here. I see the transaction via RPC and via GUI we special case it ... I have a tendency to say I dislike that GUI behavior. What do you think?\n",
